'''湯姆·克魯斯'''（英語：Tom Cruise，1962年7月3日－）全名'''湯瑪斯·克魯斯·馬波瑟四世'''（英語：Thomas Cruise Mapother IV），是知名美國籍男演員及電影製片人。作為世界上收入最多的演員之一，<ref name=Block>{{cite book|editor1-last=Block|editor1-first=Alex Ben|editor2-last=Wilson|editor2-first=Lucy Autrey|year=2010|title=George Lucas's Blockbusting: A Decade-By-Decade Survey of Timeless Movies Including Untold Secrets of Their Financial and Cultural Success|publisher=[[HarperCollins|HarperCollins]]|isbn=9780061778896|pages=[https://archive.org/details/georgelucassbloc00alex/page/616 616–617, 714–715, 824–825 & 832]|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/georgelucassbloc00alex/page/616}}</ref> 他獲得了多項榮譽，包含三次[[金球獎|金球獎]]和[[金棕榈奖|榮譽金棕榈奖]]，以及三次[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]和[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]提名。[[汤姆·克鲁斯作品列表|他的電影]]在北美擁有超過40億票房，而在全球擁有超過110億美元票房，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Top 100 Stars in Leading Roles at the Worldwide Box Office|url=https://m.the-numbers.com/box-office-star-records/worldwide/lifetime-acting/top-grossing-leading-stars}}</ref> 使他成為有史以來[[最高電影票房演員列表|票房最高的巨星]]。<ref>{{cite web| url= https://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/?view=Actor&sort=sumgross&p=.htm| title= People Index| website= Box Office Mojo| access-date= August 16, 2019| archive-date= June 27, 2019| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190627001804/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/?view=Actor&sort=sumgross&p=.htm| url-status= live}}</ref>

克魯斯於1980年代開始他的演藝生涯，並在喜劇片[[保送入學|保送入學]]（1983）和動作片[[捍衛戰士|壮志凌云]]（1986）中取得突破。他因在[[金錢本色|金錢本色]]（1986）、[[雨人|雨人]]（1988）和[[生于七月四日_(电影)|生于七月四日]]（1989）的演出而備受好評。因其在生於七月四日對{{le|羅恩·科維奇|Ron Kovic}}的刻畫，使他獲得第一個[[金球獎|金球獎]]和[[奧斯卡最佳男主角|奧斯卡最佳男主角]]提名。作為1990年代好萊塢的領軍人物，他出演了多部票房大賣的電影，包括劇情片[[軍官與魔鬼|軍官與魔鬼]]（1992）、驚悚片[[黑色豪門企業|黑色豪門企業]]（1993）、恐怖片[[夜访吸血鬼|夜访吸血鬼]]（1994）和愛情片[[征服情海|征服情海]]（1996）。出於他在征服情海的演出，他再次獲得金球獎最佳男主角和奧斯卡獎提名。

克魯斯因其在劇情片[[木兰花_(电影)|木兰花]]（1999）中飾演一名演說家的演出，第三次獲得金球獎和[[奥斯卡最佳男配角奖|奥斯卡最佳男配角奖]]提名。從那時開始，他主要在科幻或動作電影中演出，確立自己動作第一巨星的地位，他在[[不可能的任務_(電影系列)|不可能的任務系列]]電影中八次飾演[[伊森·韓特|伊森·韓特]]。他在該類型的著名演出包含[[香草天空|香草天空]]（2001）、[[少数派报告_(电影)|少数派报告]]（2002）、[[最後武士|最後武士]]（2003）、[[落日殺神|落日殺神]]（2004）、[[世界大战_(2005年电影)|世界大战]]（2005）、[[騎士出任務|騎士出任務]]（2010）、[[侠探杰克|侠探杰克]]（2012）、[[遺落戰境|遺落戰境]]（2013）、[[明日边缘|明日边缘]]（2014）和[[捍衛戰士：獨行俠|捍衛戰士：獨行俠]]（2022）。

克魯斯曾經與[[咪咪·羅傑斯|咪咪·羅傑斯]]、[[妮可·基嫚|妮可·基嫚]]和[[姬蒂·荷姆絲|姬蒂·荷姆絲]]結婚。他有三名子女，其中兩名為收養，一名為與荷姆絲所生。

== 演藝事業 ==
2017年8月，克魯斯在[[伦敦|倫敦]]趕拍新片《[[不可能的任務：全面瓦解|不可能的任務：全面瓦解]]》期間，拍攝跳樓戲失手，腳踝關節至少兩度骨折，預計需休養數個月才能康復<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/foreign/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82abc/%E6%B9%AF%E5%91%8A%E9%AD%AF%E6%96%AF%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%9D%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%88?cat=2 |title=湯告魯斯腳踝骨折停工數月 |accessdate=2017-08-16 |archive-date=2017-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816110046/http://bka.mpweekly.com/focus/foreign/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82abc/%E6%B9%AF%E5%91%8A%E9%AD%AF%E6%96%AF%E8%85%B3%E8%B8%9D%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%88?cat=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在1994年的電影《[[夜訪吸血鬼|夜訪吸血鬼]]》里，他主演的萊斯特高貴而狂野，可謂湯姆克魯斯個人演技的顛峰作之一。一別以往陽光硬漢的演出，展現了雌雄同體的精湛演技。原著作者安·萊絲起初中意的人選並非湯姆克魯斯，甚至在正式宣布由湯姆克魯斯接演萊斯特後大聲抨擊，然而在電影正式上映後，安·萊絲改口：「湯姆克魯斯完全演出了我心目中的萊斯特!」

2020年9月，正在拍攝中的克魯斯動作電影代表系列最新作《[[不可能的任務：致命清算_第一章|不可能的任務：致命清算 第一章]]》，由於[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]停工5個月<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tom Cruise Tears Into ‘Mission: Impossible 7’ Crew for Not Following COVID-19 Safety Protocols|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/tom-cruise-yells-mission-impossible-7-crew-covid-19-guidelines-1234854675/|access-date=2021-05-18|date=2020-12-16|last=Shafer|first=Ellise|work=Variety|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220104043120/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/tom-cruise-yells-mission-impossible-7-crew-covid-19-guidelines-1234854675/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。及後為免拍攝再受阻礙，決定以50萬英鎊租借郵輪讓劇組暫住及代步<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tom Cruise Rents $670K Cruise Ship to Keep ‘Mission: Impossible 7’ Filming Afloat|url=https://movieweb.com/mission-impossible-7-tom-cruise-ship-rental/|access-date=2021-05-18|date=2020-09-01|work=Movieweb|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211014193909/https://movieweb.com/mission-impossible-7-tom-cruise-ship-rental/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Tom Cruise rents £500k cruise ship to prevent more Mission: Impossible 7 filming delays|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-norway-filming-release-date-a9700266.html|access-date=2021-05-18|date=2020-09-02|work=The Independent|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210705010536/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/tom-cruise-mission-impossible-norway-filming-release-date-a9700266.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年12月16日，克魯斯因[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]所以造成電影《不可能的任務：致命清算 第一章》已延期多時，再加上拍攝時的工作人員沒有做好防疫措施，造成克魯斯暴怒，氣的大罵「他X的滾蛋」。<ref>{{Cite web|title=阿湯哥片場暴怒飆粗口 喬治克隆尼緩頰「他沒有錯」|url=https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10090/5100001|accessdate=2021-03-27|last=聯合新聞網|work=噓！星聞|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101000116/https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10090/5100001|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=「不可能7」劇組疏離防疫 阿湯哥暴怒嗆「他X的滾蛋」|url=https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10090/5096235|accessdate=2021-03-27|last=聯合新聞網|work=噓！星聞|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128204959/https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10090/5096235|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=粗口飆罵「他X的滾蛋」 阿湯哥暴怒2分鐘音檔流出│TVBS新聞網|url=https://news.tvbs.com.tw/entertainment/1433583|accessdate=2021-03-27|last=TVBS|work=TVBS|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2020-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222132713/https://news.tvbs.com.tw/entertainment/1433583|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=阿湯哥爆為防疫粗口飆罵劇組人員 音檔外流：他X的給我滾 - 娛樂|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201216003424-260404|accessdate=2021-03-27|last=中時新聞網|work=中時新聞網|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126100652/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201216003424-260404|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2021年6月，《不可能的任務：致命清算 第一章》因爲有劇組成員新冠病毒檢測陽性被迫再次暫停拍攝。<ref>{{Cite web|title=《碟中諜7》因劇組成員新冠檢測陽性暫停拍攝|url=https://www.163.com/dy/article/GBLRC58V0514EMD3.html|access-date=2021-07-10|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711231234/https://www.163.com/dy/article/GBLRC58V0514EMD3.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
汤姆·克鲁斯的父親是國防電子工程師，母親是特殊教育教師，他父親脾氣很差常毆打他，12歲的時候父母離婚。湯姆克魯斯有[[英國裔美國人|英國]]、[[德國裔美國人|德國]]與[[愛爾蘭裔美國人|愛爾蘭]]血統，年輕時曾考慮當[[天主教|天主教]][[神父|神父]]，也曾在足球隊踢球但因喝酒被開除，在中學時開始對演戲感興趣，湯姆克魯斯第一部參加的電影是1981年《無盡的愛》與《熄燈號》。曾患有[[閱讀障礙|閱讀障礙]]的疾病， 但現已大幅改善。

== 關係 ==
克魯斯已結婚和離婚三次，有三個孩子（兩個收養和一個親生）。

=== 咪咪·羅傑斯 ===
1987年5月9日，汤姆·克鲁斯與女演員[[咪咪·羅傑斯|咪咪·羅傑斯]]結婚。他們於1990年2月4日離婚。羅傑斯把克魯斯介紹給科學教。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.radaronline.com/from-the-magazine/2005/08/the_passion_of_tom_cruise_excerpt.php |title = THE PASSION OF TOM CRUISE |author = Kim Masters |date = 2005-08-15 |publisher = Radar |language = en |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061019111857/http://www.radaronline.com/from-the-magazine/2005/08/the_passion_of_tom_cruise_excerpt.php |archivedate = 2006-10-19 }}</ref>

=== 妮歌·潔曼 ===
克魯斯和澳洲著名女演員，[[妮歌·潔曼|妮歌·潔曼]]於拍攝電影《{{link-en|雷霆壯志|Days of Thunder}}》（1990年）時認識。他們於1990年12月24日結婚。克魯斯及潔曼共有1名養女及1名養子，分別是伊莎貝拉（Isabella）和康納（Connor）。2001年2月，克魯斯在潔曼不知不覺地懷孕時提起離婚。2007年，潔曼澄清了在與克魯斯結婚時早期流產的傳言，在接受採訪時說：「這是錯誤的報導」，並解釋說她實際上有[[異位妊娠|異位妊娠]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity/a934/nicole-kidman-interview/ |title = Nicole Kidman Tells It Like It Is |author = Meryl Gordon |date = 2007-11-11 |publisher = Marie Claire |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-15 |archive-date = 2017-04-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170428025334/http://www.marieclaire.com/celebrity/a934/nicole-kidman-interview/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>在她下一段與[[齊斯·厄本|齊斯·厄本]]的婚姻之前，潔曼談到了她仍然愛着克魯斯。她在2006年說：「他曾是大明星，現在還是。對我來說，他只是湯，但是對於別人來說，他是大明星。但他對我很好，我愛他。我還愛著他。」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.today.com/id/12690470/ns/today-entertainment/t/nicole-kidman-says-she-still-loves-tom-cruise/#.WPJls9KGOUk |title = Nicole Kidman says she still loves Tom Cruise |date = 2006-05-09 |publisher = today.com |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-15 |archive-date = 2017-09-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170903120221/http://www.today.com/id/12690470/ns/today-entertainment/t/nicole-kidman-says-she-still-loves-tom-cruise/#.WPJls9KGOUk |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 與佩内洛普·克魯兹和納贊寧·波妮阿蒂約會 ===
克魯斯的下一段浪漫關聯是與女演員[[佩内洛普·克魯兹|佩内洛普·克魯兹]]交往，他們在《[[魂離情外天|魂離情外天]]》（2001年）聯合演出。其關係在2004年結束。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3570639.stm |title = Cruise and Cruz end relationship |date = 2004-03-26 |publisher = BBC News |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-16 |archive-date = 2017-01-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170106083855/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3570639.stm |dead-url = no }}</ref>2012年10月出版的《[[名利場_(雜誌)|名利場]]》中的一篇文章指出，有幾個消息來源表示，在與克魯斯分手後，科學教會啟動了一個秘密計劃，替克魯斯尋找新女友。文章稱科學教女演員的一系列「面試」導致與伊朗女演員{{link-en|納贊寧·波妮阿蒂|Nazanin Boniadi}}短暫的關係，她其後便離開了科學教。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2012/09/tom-cruise-scientology-marriage-katie-holmes |title = TOM CRUISE'S SCIENTOLOGY MARRIAGES: THE SECRET WIFE-AUDITIONING PROCESS BEFORE KATIE HOLMES, REVEALED |date = 2012-09-01 |publisher = Vanity Fair |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-16 |archive-date = 2017-04-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170409230017/http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2012/09/tom-cruise-scientology-marriage-katie-holmes |dead-url = no }}</ref>

科學教教會和克魯斯的律師發出強烈的措辭否認和威脅起訴，指責《名利場》的「劣質新聞」和「宗教偏見」。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/scientology-threatens-vanity-fair-over-tom-cruise-auditions-claims-8122450.html |title = Scientology threatens Vanity Fair over Tom Cruise 'auditions' claims |author = Guy Adams |date = 2012-09-11 |publisher = The Independent |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-16 |archive-date = 2017-03-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170317063247/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/scientology-threatens-vanity-fair-over-tom-cruise-auditions-claims-8122450.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>記者{{link-en|羅傑·弗里德曼|Roger Friedman}}後來報導，他曾收到來自導演和前科學教教徒[[保羅·哈吉斯|保羅·哈吉斯]]的電子郵件來證實這個故事。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.showbiz411.com/2012/09/02/oscar-winner-paul-haggis-on-tom-cruise-scientology-girlfriend |title = Exclusive: Oscar Winner Paul Haggis on Tom Cruise Scientology Girlfriend: “I'm appalled that any church would treat its parishioners this way” |author = Roger Friedman |date = 2012-09-02 |publisher = Showbiz411.com |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-16 |archive-date = 2017-03-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170314144635/http://www.showbiz411.com/2012/09/02/oscar-winner-paul-haggis-on-tom-cruise-scientology-girlfriend |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tom-cruise-lawyer-on-vanity-fair-expose-tired-old-lies/ |title = Tom Cruise lawyer on Vanity Fair expose: 'Tired old lies' |date = 2012-09-05 |publisher = CBS News |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-16 |archive-date = 2017-04-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170416221257/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tom-cruise-lawyer-on-vanity-fair-expose-tired-old-lies/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 凱蒂·霍爾姆斯 ===
[[File:Tom_Cruise_&_Katie_Holmes_WHCAD.jpg|thumb]]]]
2005年4月，克魯斯開始跟女演員，[[凱蒂·霍爾姆斯|凱蒂·霍爾姆斯]]約會。他在电视节目[[Oprah_Winfrey_Show|Oprah Winfrey Show]]中，狂熱地表达对凱蒂的爱，甚至兩次跳上沙发，脫序行為在當時引起了很大爭議。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2005/06/02/movies/02crui.html?ex=1275364800&en=5bee0745ec59eea3&ei=5090&partner=rssuserland&emc=rss |title=The New York Times  Movies  How Personal Is Too Personal for a Star Like Tom Cruise |accessdate=2012-05-22 |archive-date=2006-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060621003415/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/06/02/movies/02crui.html?ex=1275364800&en=5bee0745ec59eea3&ei=5090&partner=rssuserland&emc=rss |dead-url=no }}</ref>；同年6月17日，克魯斯宣佈霍爾姆斯接受了他在[[艾菲爾鐵塔|艾菲爾鐵塔]]的求婚；2006年11月18日，他們於意大利首都罗马附近的[[奥迪斯卡契城堡|奥迪斯卡契城堡]]結婚。兩人亦被人稱為「TomKat」。克魯斯和凱蒂在2006年迎接了他們的女兒。2012年6月29日，兩人在結婚五年半后離婚。<ref>{{cite news|title=Tom Cruise, Katie Holmes to divorce|url=http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2012/06/29/report-tom-cruise-katie-holmes-set-to-divorce/?|publisher=CNN Entertainment|date=June 29, 2012|accessdate=June 29, 2012|archive-date=2012-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120629212600/http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2012/06/29/report-tom-cruise-katie-holmes-set-to-divorce/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Heyman|first=J.D.|title=Tom Cruise and Katie Holmes Are Divorcing|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20608003,00.html|work=People|date=June 29, 2012|accessdate=June 29, 2012|archive-date=2012-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120629171231/http://www.people.com/people/article/0%2C%2C20608003%2C00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這也是湯姆的第三次離婚<ref>{{cite web|title=Tom Cruise and Katie Holmes File for Divorce|url=http://www.backstageol.com/celebrity/tom-cruise-and-katie-holmes-file-for-divorce/|first=Jonathan|last=Stenvall|publisher=BackstageOL|date=June 29, 2012|accessdate=June 29, 2012|archive-date=2012-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120701220255/http://www.backstageol.com/celebrity/tom-cruise-and-katie-holmes-file-for-divorce/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

汤姆·克鲁斯在2013年11月5日告鲍尔传媒集团的法庭文档中正式阐述凯蒂否认离婚和科学教有关。同时，在《[[時人_(杂志)|人物]]》杂志的报道中，他对小报的诽谤进行辟谣，科学教从来不是离婚的理由。

凱蒂·霍爾姆斯和湯姆·克魯斯在2012年6月離婚後，與影帝傑米福克斯走很近，2017年9月在馬里布海灘牽手踏浪的照片被公開，這段維持4年的地下情終於見光，而傑米福克斯是因電影《[[落日殺神|落日殺神]]》( Collateral ) 而與湯姆克魯斯結緣並認識了 13 年的好友。

== 科學教（山達基） ==
[[File:Tom_Cruise_and_Mimi_Rogers.jpg|thumb]]
汤姆·克鲁斯曾公开发言支持[[山达基|科學教教会]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/showbiz/1791617.stm |title=BBC News  SHOWBIZ  Cruise lobbies over Scientology |accessdate=2012-05-22 |archive-date=2009-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090111115127/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/showbiz/1791617.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於1986年透過第一任妻子[[咪咪·羅傑斯|咪咪·羅傑斯]]加入山達基<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://tonyortega.org/2015/04/12/how-scientology-broke-up-tom-cruise-and-mimi-rogers-the-story-you-havent-heard/ |title = How Scientology broke up Tom Cruise and Mimi Rogers: The story you haven't heard |author = Tony Ortega |date = April 12, 2015 |publisher = The Underground Bunker |language = en |accessdate = 2015-12-30 |archive-date = 2015-12-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151231171914/http://tonyortega.org/2015/04/12/how-scientology-broke-up-tom-cruise-and-mimi-rogers-the-story-you-havent-heard/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，而且他說明過自己成功克服[[閱讀障礙|閱讀障礙]]主要歸功於[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]的教學技術{{link-en|Study Tech|Study Tech}}<ref>{{cite news|title=Cruise credits Scientology for his success|publisher=msnbc.com|language=en|date=May 24, 2005|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/7968809/|accessdate=2015-12-30|archive-date=2008-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080312073829/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/7968809/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1998年他将说他是[[同性恋|同性恋]]的Daily Express告上法庭。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/203779.stm |title=BBC News  Entertainment  Cruise and Kidman win libel case |accessdate=2012-05-22 |archive-date=2009-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090503095051/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/203779.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===  克魯斯對科學教的擁護 ===
除了推廣各種-{}-計劃來向人介紹科學教外，克魯斯也參加將科學教於歐洲被承認為宗教的運動。在2005年，湯姆·克魯斯向法國巴黎議員[[尼古拉·薩爾科齊|尼古拉·薩爾科齊]]及{{link-en|Jean-Claude Gaudin|Jean-Claude Gaudin}}進行遊說，但遭受巴黎市議會指責科學教是一個令人不安的教派，而克魯斯更是當中的激進分子，並全面抵制他。<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.examiner.ie/breaking/story.asp?j=182470131&p=y8z47x994&n=182471074&x= |title=Paris snubs Scientology 'militant' Cruise |language=en |work=Irish Examiner |date=July 13, 2005 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>

克魯斯與其他教徒成立了{{link-en|New York Rescue Workers Detoxification Project|New York Rescue Workers Detoxification Project}}，籌集捐款給該計劃所屬的市中心區醫療組織（Downtown Medical），以協助[[九一一襲擊事件|九一一襲擊事件]]的救援人員進行[[淨化程式|排毒治療]]，此舉動引發了消防員對該計劃的批評<ref>O'Donnell, Michelle (October 4, 2003). [http://www.nytimes.com/2003/10/04/nyregion/04DETO.html?ex=1148011200&en=c46507c25827d1c3&ei=5070 "Scientologist's Treatments Lure Firefighters"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/10/04/nyregion/04DETO.html?ex=1148011200&en=c46507c25827d1c3&ei=5070 |date=20160618160620 }}.The New York Times.</ref>，認為其真正目的是趁機吸引人參加山達基。<ref>{{cite news |first=Roger |last=Friedman |title=Tom Cruise Can't Put Out These Fires |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,238238,00.html#2 |publisher=Fox News |language=en |date=December 22, 2006 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070109070250/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0%2C2933%2C238238%2C00.html#2 |archivedate=2007年1月9日 }}</ref>

對於此類活動，科學教主席[[大衛·密斯凱維吉|大衛·密斯凱維吉]]於2004年頒贈科學教的勳章給湯姆·克魯斯，以讚揚他對-{教會}-的貢獻。<ref>{{cite web |title= What Katie Didn't Know |work= Vanity Fair |language= en |date= October 2012 |author= Maureen Orth |url= http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2012/10/katie-holmes-divorce-scientology |accessdate= 2015-12-30 |archive-date= 2015-12-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151225081707/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2012/10/katie-holmes-divorce-scientology |dead-url= no }}</ref>

=== 對精神病學的批評 ===
2004年1月，克魯斯做了一個有爭議的聲明「我認為精神病學應該被定為不合法」。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Desai|first=Nimesh|title=Antipsychiatry: Meeting the challenge|journal=Indian Journal of Psychiatry|date=Oct–Dec 2005|volume=47|issue=4|pages=185–187|doi=10.4103/0019-5545.43048|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2921130/|accessdate=2015-12-31|pmid=20711302|pmc=2921130|archive-date=2014-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907224453/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2921130/|dead-url=no}}</ref>更進一步的爭議是在2005年，當時克魯斯公開地批評[[波姬·小絲|波姬·小絲]]使用[[抗抑鬱藥|抗抑鬱藥]]叫[[帕羅西汀|帕羅西汀]]（Paroxetine）來治療[[產後抑鬱症|產後抑鬱症]]，他宣稱從來沒有所謂的{{link-en|化學失衡|Chemical imbalance}}（由精神病引起的一種假說），而[[精神病學|精神病學]]只是一門[[偽科學|偽科學]]，因為眾所周知山達基教一向反對精神病學及精神科藥物。其後波姬回應克魯斯「應該只顧去從外星人的手中拯救整個世界，然後就讓一些正在經歷產後抑鬱症的女人決定哪一個的治療方法適合她們自己」（原文："Tom should stick to saving the world from aliens and let women who are experiencing postpartum depression decide what treatment options are best for them"）。<ref>{{cite news |language = en |url = http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1067822,00.html |title = Brooke Shields Lashes Out at Tom Cruise |publisher = People |date = 2005-06-02 |accessdate = 2015-12-31 |archive-date = 2015-11-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151113165647/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1067822,00.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>這引起了克魯斯與{{link-en|馬特勞爾|Matt Lauer}}在2005年6月24日[[全國廣播公司|全國廣播公司]]（NBC）的[[今日秀|今日秀]]之中進行激烈爭論<ref>[http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/8344309/ "In tense moment, Cruise calls Lauer 'glib] {{Wayback|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/8344309/ |date=20090201000940 }} msnbc.com. (2005-06-28)</ref>。

醫學權威機構認為克魯斯的評論是對精神病的一大污點<ref>{{cite news |language = en |author = Max Pemberton |url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/health/alternative-medicine/3338404/Alien-soul-theory-is-no-cure-for-depression.html |title = Alien soul theory is no cure for depression |publisher = The Daily Telegraph |date = 2006-04-17 |accessdate = 2015-12-31 |archive-date = 2015-11-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151107042114/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/health/alternative-medicine/3338404/Alien-soul-theory-is-no-cure-for-depression.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>，而波姬稱克魯斯的評論傷害了所有母親<ref>{{cite news |language = en |author = Brooke Shields |url = http://www.nytimes.com/2005/07/01/opinion/war-of-words.html |title = War of Words |publisher = The New York Times |date = 2005-07-01 |accessdate = 2015-12-31 |archive-date = 2015-12-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151219093223/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/07/01/opinion/war-of-words.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。直到2006年8月，克魯斯才親自向波姬致歉<ref>{{cite news |language = en |url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2006-09-02-shields-cruise_x.htm |title = Shields: Cruise apology was 'heartfelt' |publisher = USA Today |date = 2006-09-02 |accessdate = 2015-12-31 |archive-date = 2016-03-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043501/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2006-09-02-shields-cruise_x.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

由於克魯斯的反精神病學的言論和活動，開始導致與他拍攝《[[強戰世界|強戰世界]]》的導演[[史提芬·史匹堡|史提芬·史匹堡]]產生不和，煩厭克魯斯在訪問期間替山達基作宣傳多過電影。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://entertainment.myway.com/celebgossip/pgsix/id/09_21_2005_1.html |title = SPIELBERG IN CRUISE MELTDOWN |date = 2005-09-21 |publisher = myway.com |language = en |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050930235723/http://entertainment.myway.com/celebgossip/pgsix/id/09_21_2005_1.html |archivedate = 2005-09-30 }}</ref>

=== YouTube影片的刪除 ===
{{see also2|{{link-en|Project Chanology|Project Chanology}}}}
2008年1月15日，一段由科學教訪問湯·克魯斯的影片被上載至[[YouTube|YouTube]]，片中主要提及克魯斯討論科學教對他自己的重要性。<ref>{{cite news |language = en |author = Catherine Elsworth |url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1575760/Tom-Cruise-Scientology-video-leaked-on-web.html |title = Tom Cruise Scientology video leaked on web |publisher = The Telegraph |date = 2008-01-16 |accessdate = 2016-01-05 |archive-date = 2015-11-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151114081034/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1575760/Tom-Cruise-Scientology-video-leaked-on-web.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>科學教會聲稱這影片是「被盜竊及剪輯過」，剪掉了其餘三小時的片段包括多名科學教成員。<ref>{{cite news |language = en |url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2008/01/23/report-church-scientology-slams-german-tabloid-for-publishing-comments.html |title = Report: Church of Scientology Slams German Tabloid for Publishing Comments Comparing Tom Cruise to Nazi Minister |publisher = FOX News Network |date = 2008-01-23 |accessdate = 2016-01-05 |archive-date = 2016-03-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308073030/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2008/01/23/report-church-scientology-slams-german-tabloid-for-publishing-comments.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>YouTube曾經在被起訴的威脅下移除該影片。<ref>{{cite news |language = en |author = Robert Vamosi |url = http://www.cnet.com/news/anonymous-hackers-take-on-the-church-of-scientology/ |title = Anonymous hackers take on the Church of Scientology |publisher = CNET Networks |date = 2008-01-25 |accessdate = 2016-01-05 |archive-date = 2016-01-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102161318/http://www.cnet.com/news/anonymous-hackers-take-on-the-church-of-scientology/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

其後引起了黑客組織[[匿名者|匿名者]]（Anonymous）的不滿，而成立了一個反山達基的活動「{{link-en|Project Chanology|Project Chanology}}」，目的是驅除所有科學教在網絡上的運作。<ref>{{cite news |language = en |author = Patrick Barkham |url = http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2008/feb/04/news |title = Hackers declare war on Scientologists amid claims of heavy-handed Cruise control |publisher = The Guardian |date = 2008-02-04 |accessdate = 2016-01-05 |archive-date = 2016-01-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160102161315/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2008/feb/04/news |dead-url = no }}</ref>後來該訪問影片被發現並沒有違反版權法，實際上是屬於[[合理使用|合理使用]]。而影片在YouTube上已被恢復，至今仍然可以觀看。

=== 山達基在克魯斯的人際關係上所據稱的影響 ===
2013年，克魯斯闡述前妻[[凱蒂·霍爾姆斯|凱蒂·霍爾姆斯]]與他離婚有部分原因是為了保護女兒蘇瑞（Suri）免受科學教騷擾，而他也說蘇瑞不會是科學教成員。<ref>{{cite news |language = en |author = Stephanie Marcus |url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/11/08/tom-cruise-katie-holmes-protect-suri-scientology_n_4240715.html?ir=Entertainment |title = Tom Cruise Admits Katie Holmes Divorced Him To Protect Suri From Scientology |publisher = The Huffington Post |date = 2013-11-08 |accessdate = 2016-01-05 |archive-date = 2015-11-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117132658/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/11/08/tom-cruise-katie-holmes-protect-suri-scientology_n_4240715.html?ir=Entertainment |dead-url = no }}</ref>

根據2015年的紀錄片《[[解密科學教|解密科學教]]》（''Going Clear: Scientology and the Prison of Belief''）中，宣稱克魯斯利用[[海洋機構|海洋機構]]的人員作為免費勞工。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.businessinsider.com/tom-cruises-secret-scientology-girlfriend-nazanin-boniadi-2015-3 |title = The crazy story of how Scientology allegedly once groomed a girlfriend for Tom Cruise — and then tore them apart |author = Aly Weisman |date = 2015-04-01 |publisher = Business Insider |language = en |accessdate = 2016-01-05 |archive-date = 2015-12-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222081113/http://www.businessinsider.com/tom-cruises-secret-scientology-girlfriend-nazanin-boniadi-2015-3 |dead-url = no }}</ref>在紀錄片中，克魯斯的前核數師{{link-en|馬克·賴斯本|Mark Rathbun}}聲稱[[妮歌·潔曼|妮歌·潔曼]]受到克魯斯和[[密斯凱維吉|密斯凱維吉]]竊聽（克魯斯的律師否認），原因是她被科學教視為「{{link-en|抑制者|Suppressive Person}}」（Suppressive Person）。<ref>{{cite news |language = en |author = Philip Sherwell |url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/11370754/Scientology-leaders-ordered-Nicole-Kidman-wiretap-during-Tom-Cruise-marriage.html |title = Scientology leaders 'ordered Nicole Kidman wiretap' during Tom Cruise marriage |publisher = The Telegraph |date = 2015-01-26 |accessdate = 2016-01-05 |archive-date = 2015-12-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151223044602/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/11370754/Scientology-leaders-ordered-Nicole-Kidman-wiretap-during-Tom-Cruise-marriage.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.eonline.com/news/618897/controversial-scientology-documentary-alleges-tom-cruise-wiretapped-nicole-kidman-s-phone-church-slams-claims |title = Controversial Scientology Documentary Alleges Tom Cruise Wiretapped Nicole Kidman's Phone, Church Slams Claims |author = Lily Harrison |date = 2015-01-28 |publisher = E! Online |language = en |accessdate = 2016-01-05 |archive-date = 2015-12-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151213122621/http://www.eonline.com/news/618897/controversial-scientology-documentary-alleges-tom-cruise-wiretapped-nicole-kidman-s-phone-church-slams-claims |dead-url = no }}</ref>（山達基術語，壓抑者意思為會壓抑周遭其他人的人）

